<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
  <title>FAQ — Classic Academy</title>

  <!-- SEO -->
  <meta name="description"
    content="Frequently asked questions about Classic Academy plans, onboarding, admissions, and finance modules." />
  <meta name="robots" content="index,follow,max-snippet:-1,max-image-preview:large,max-video-preview:-1" />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#4a90e2" />
  <link rel="canonical" href="/faq" />
  <meta property="og:type" content="website" />
  <meta property="og:title" content="FAQ — Classic Academy" />
  <meta property="og:description"
    content="Frequently asked questions about Classic Academy plans, onboarding, admissions, and finance modules." />
  <meta property="og:url" content="/faq" />
  <meta property="og:image" content="img/hero.png" />
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image" />
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="FAQ — Classic Academy" />
  <meta name="twitter:description"
    content="Frequently asked questions about Classic Academy plans, onboarding, admissions, and finance modules." />
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="img/hero.png" />

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    :root {
      --primary: #4a90e2;
      --accent: #d97800;
      --highlight: #009f8b;

      --ink: #0f172a;
      --muted: #475569;

      --page-pad: clamp(1rem, 4vw, 6rem);
      --section-gap: clamp(1.2rem, 2.6vw, 2rem);

      --shadow2: 0 18px 50px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      --shadow3: 0 10px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);

      --radius: 22px;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      background: #e0f7fa;
      color: #333;
      overflow-x: clip;
      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;
      padding-top: 112px;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding-top: 102px;
      }
    }

    /* LOADER (same style as main) */
    #loader {
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      background: #e0f7fa;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      z-index: 9999;
      padding: 1.2rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .academylogo {
      width: min(220px, 70vw);
    }

    .academylogo img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      display: block;
    }

    .loader {
      position: relative;
      width: 18px;
      height: 28px;
      perspective: 500px;
      animation: flip 2s infinite;
    }

    .loader:nth-child(3) {
      animation-delay: 0.2s;
    }

    .loader:nth-child(4) {
      animation-delay: 0.4s;
    }

    .loader:nth-child(5) {
      animation-delay: 0.6s;
    }

    .loader:nth-child(6) {
      animation-delay: 0.8s;
    }

    .face {
      position: absolute;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      backface-visibility: hidden;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }

    .front {
      background: var(--primary);
    }

    .back {
      background: #d35400;
      transform: rotateY(180deg);
    }

    @keyframes flip {

      0%,
      100% {
        transform: rotateY(0deg);
      }

      50% {
        transform: rotateY(180deg);
      }
    }

    /* NAVBAR (same as main) */
    .header {
      position: fixed;
      top: 14px;
      left: var(--page-pad);
      right: var(--page-pad);
      padding: .65rem .85rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .70);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .78);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      box-shadow: 0 16px 46px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: .8rem;
      z-index: 2000;
    }

    .brand {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .75rem;
      min-width: 0;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .85);
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .brand-txt {
      display: grid;
      line-height: 1.05;
      min-width: 0;
    }

    .brand-name {
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      color: var(--ink);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .brand-sub {
      font-size: .86rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      white-space: nowrap;
      overflow: hidden;
      text-overflow: ellipsis;
    }

    .navbar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .35rem;
    }

    .navbar a {
      padding: .55rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      transition: background .2s ease, transform .2s ease, color .2s ease;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .navbar a:hover {
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .10);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .nav-pill {
      border: 1px solid rgba(74, 144, 226, .35);
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .10);
      color: #0f172a !important;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .nav-pill:hover {
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .18);
      border-color: rgba(74, 144, 226, .45);
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: .55rem;
      flex: 0 0 auto;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: .45rem;
      padding: 0.72rem 1rem;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: 1px solid var(--primary);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      transition: background-color .25s ease, transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(74, 144, 226, .18);
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      background-color: transparent;
      color: var(--primary);
      transform: translateY(-1px);
      box-shadow: 0 14px 34px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
    }

    .btn.ghost {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      color: var(--ink);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
    }

    .btn.ghost:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .88);
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .btn-sm {
      padding: .55rem .8rem !important;
      font-size: .95rem !important;
      box-shadow: none !important;
    }

    .menu-btn {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .78);
      display: none;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
    }

    .menu-btn i {
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .brand-sub {
        display: none;
      }

      .menu-btn {
        display: inline-flex;
      }

      .navbar {
        position: absolute;
        top: calc(100% + .65rem);
        left: 0;
        right: 0;
        margin: 0 .25rem;
        padding: .75rem;
        background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .96);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .35);
        border-radius: 20px;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        display: grid;
        gap: .4rem;
        transform: translateY(-8px);
        opacity: 0;
        pointer-events: none;
        transition: transform .2s ease, opacity .2s ease;
      }

      .navbar.active {
        transform: translateY(0);
        opacity: 1;
        pointer-events: auto;
      }

      .navbar a {
        color: #fff;
        border-radius: 16px;
        padding: .85rem .85rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .08);
      }

      .navbar a:hover {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .14);
        transform: none;
        color: #fff;
      }

      .nav-pill {
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .18);
        border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, .35);
        color: #fff !important;
      }
    }

    /* REVEAL */
    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(14px);
      transition: all .7s ease;
    }

    .reveal.in {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
      .reveal {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: none;
        transition: none;
      }

      * {
        scroll-behavior: auto !important;
      }
    }

    /* INNER PAGE: HERO + FAQ */
    .kicker {
      display: inline-flex;
      gap: .55rem;
      align-items: center;
      color: #1b2a4e;
      font-weight: 900;
      padding: .45rem .8rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .82);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .90);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .08);
      width: fit-content;
    }

    .about-hero {
      margin: 0 var(--page-pad);
      border-radius: 26px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .28);
      backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .55);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow2);
      padding: 2rem 2rem;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr .9fr;
      gap: 1.4rem;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .about-hero h1 {
      margin: .7rem 0 .55rem 0;
      font-size: clamp(1.65rem, 2.4vw, 2.2rem);
      color: var(--ink);
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      line-height: 1.15;
    }

    .about-hero p {
      margin: 0;
      color: #334155;
      max-width: 65ch;
    }

    .about-hero .actions {
      margin-top: 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      gap: .6rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .about-hero .media {
      border-radius: 22px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: rgba(74, 144, 226, .12);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .75);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      min-height: 260px;
    }

    .about-hero .media img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      object-fit: cover;
      display: block;
    }

    .page-wrap {
      margin: 0 var(--page-pad);
      padding: 2.2rem 0 2.8rem 0;
    }

    .page-head {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 920px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.2rem auto;
    }

    .page-head h2 {
      margin: .8rem 0 .35rem 0;
      color: var(--ink);
      font-size: clamp(1.35rem, 2vw, 2rem);
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
    }

    .page-head p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .faq-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 1.2rem;
      margin-top: 1.1rem;
    }

    .faq-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .72);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, .85);
      border-radius: 22px;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(15, 23, 42, .10);
      padding: .9rem .95rem;
    }

    .faq-q {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 1rem;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--ink);
      padding: .2rem .15rem;
    }

    .faq-q i {
      color: var(--primary);
      margin-top: .3rem;
      transition: transform .2s ease;
    }

    .faq-card.open .faq-q i {
      transform: rotate(45deg);
    }

    .faq-a {
      max-height: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      transition: max-height .28s ease;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
      padding: 0 .15rem;
    }

    .faq-card.open .faq-a {
      max-height: 520px;
      margin-top: .45rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .about-hero {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .faq-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    /* FOOTER (same layout/width feel) */
    .footer {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      border-radius: 25px;
      margin: 2rem var(--page-pad);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: space-between;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .footer div {
      margin: 1rem;
      flex: 1 1 200px;
      min-width: 200px;
    }

    .footer h4 {
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      margin-bottom: .8rem;
      color: var(--ink);
    }

    .footer p {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }

    .footer ul li {
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .footer ul li a {
      color: #333;
    }

    .footer ul li a:hover {
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* Scroll to Top Button */
    #toTopBtn {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      right: 30px;
      background-color: var(--primary);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      width: 42px;
      height: 42px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      display: none;
      z-index: 1000;
      transition: background 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
    }

    #toTopBtn:hover {
      background-color: #4a90e2;
      transform: scale(1.1);
    }

    /* Floating support button */
    .shadow {
      box-shadow: 0 10px 26px rgba(15, 23, 42, .12);
    }

    .fab-container {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      align-items: center;
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 170px;
      right: 20px;
      z-index: 1200;
    }

    .fab-container:hover {
      height: 100%;
    }

    .fab-container:hover .sub-button:nth-child(2) {
      transform: translateY(-80px);
    }

    .fab-container:hover .sub-button:nth-child(3) {
      transform: translateY(-140px);
    }

    .fab-container:hover .sub-button:nth-child(4) {
      transform: translateY(-200px);
    }

    .fab-container .fab {
      position: relative;
      height: 70px;
      width: 70px;
      background-color: #4ba2ff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .fab-container .fab:before {
      content: " ";
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 35px;
      width: 35px;
      background-color: inherit;
      border-radius: 0 0 10px 0;
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .fab-container .fab .fab-content {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 50%;
      cursor: pointer;
      user-select: none;
    }

    .fab-container .fab .fab-content .material-icons {
      color: #2e2e2e;
      font-size: 48px;
    }

    .fab-container .sub-button {
      position: absolute;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      bottom: 10px;
      right: 10px;
      height: 50px;
      width: 50px;
      background-color: #4ba2ff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .fab-container .sub-button a {
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      border-radius: 50%;
    }

    .fab-container .sub-button .material-icons {
      color: #2e2e2e;
      padding-top: 6px;
    }

    .fab-container .sub-button i {
      color: #2e2e2e;
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .fab-container .sub-button:hover .material-icons,
    .fab-container .sub-button:hover i {
      color: #FEFEFE;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <!-- Loader -->
  <div id="loader">
    <div class="academylogo">
      <img src="./img/academylogo.png" alt="Classic Academy logo">
    </div>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:10px;">
      <div class="loader">
        <div class="face front"></div>
        <div class="face back"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loader">
        <div class="face front"></div>
        <div class="face back"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loader">
        <div class="face front"></div>
        <div class="face back"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loader">
        <div class="face front"></div>
        <div class="face back"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="loader">
        <div class="face front"></div>
        <div class="face back"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Nav -->
  <header class="header" id="siteHeader">
    <a href="/" class="brand" aria-label="Classic Academy Home">
      <img class="brand-mark" src="./img/academylogo.png" alt="Classic Academy logo">
      <div class="brand-txt">
        <span class="brand-name">Classic Academy</span>
        <span class="brand-sub">School management + admissions</span>
      </div>
    </a>

    <nav class="navbar" aria-label="Primary">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <a href="/about">About</a>
      <a href="/services">Features</a>
      <a href="/#testimonials">Benefits</a>
      <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="/#pricing">Join Today</a>
      <a class="nav-pill" href="/schedule">Sign In</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a href="/schedule" class="btn btn-sm"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i> Book Demo</a>
      <button id="menu-btn" class="menu-btn" aria-label="Open menu" aria-expanded="false">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-bars"></i>
      </button>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="about-hero reveal" style="margin-top: 0;">
      <div>
        <span class="kicker"><i class="fa-solid fa-sparkles"></i> Help Center</span>
        <h1>Answers to common questions.</h1>
        <p>Find quick answers about onboarding, plans, admissions, finance tracking, and support. If you need help, book
          a demo or contact us.</p>
        <div class="actions">
          <a class="btn" href="/schedule"><i class="fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i> Book Demo</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/contact"><i class="fa-solid fa-phone-volume"></i> Contact</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/#pricing"><i class="fa-solid fa-tags"></i> Pricing</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="media">
        <img src="img/hero.png" alt="Classic Academy">
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="page-wrap">
      <div class="page-head reveal">
        <span class="kicker"><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-question"></i> FAQ</span>
        <h2>Frequently asked questions</h2>
        <p>Tap a question to expand the answer.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-grid">
        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>Can we start free?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes. The School Profile package is free and includes admissions basics. You can upgrade
            anytime when you need full operations modules.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>How do upgrades work?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Plans are layered: Starter includes Profile, Standard includes Starter, Growth includes
            Standard, Premium includes everything. Upgrading unlocks additional modules.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>Does Classic Academy support invoices and receipts?</span><i
              class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes — finance tracking (invoices, receipts, balances, statements) is available on Standard
            and above.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>Do you support SMS/Email notifications?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes as an add-on. Premium can include stronger messaging workflows and portals.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>Can we manage multiple campuses?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes — multi-campus/branch support can be enabled as an add-on (typically Growth/Premium).
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>How long does onboarding take?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Most schools can start in days. We help with setup, roles, data import templates, and staff
            training.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>Can parents access a portal?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes — parent portal and messaging can be enabled as an add-on depending on your plan.</div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-card reveal">
          <div class="faq-q"><span>Do you provide support after setup?</span><i class="fa-solid fa-plus"></i></div>
          <div class="faq-a">Yes. Support continues after onboarding. You can also book a demo any time for guided help.
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <!-- Footer (same as main page) -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <div>
      <h4>About Us</h4>
      <p>We are excited to introduce our upcoming Classic Academy Plans, where schools will be categorized</p>
      <a href="https://play.google.com/store" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/7/78/Google_Play_Store_badge_EN.svg"
          style="height: 50px; width: 150px" alt="Google Play">
      </a>
